a system be call linear if the principle of superposition apply .
the principle of superposition state that the response produce by the simultaneous application of two different force function be the sum of the two individual response .
hence , for the linear system , the response to several input can be calculate by treat one input at a time and add the result .
it be this principle that allow one to build up complicated solution to the linear differential equation from simple solution .
